        <figure class="lead-img">
            <img data-src="http://cdn.theatlantic.com/assets/media/video/img/2015/09/James_Greg_thumb1/still.jpg?1441384867" class="lazyload">
            
        </figure>
    

        <h3 class="hed">How America Reacted to 'The Coddling of the American Mind'</h3>
    </a>
    <ul class="metadata">
